<title>UK: Speciality Shops finance director resigns.</title>
<headline>Speciality Shops finance director resigns.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-05-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>British property investment company Speciality Shops Plc said on Friday that its finance director David Lindop had resigned from the board.</p>
<p>The company did not give any reason behind his resignation.</p>
<p>&quot;We will soon be announcing the appointment of a new incumbent to the post who will be responsible for overseeing the financial direction of the group as it continues to press forward with its expansion plans,&quot; the company said in a statement.</p>
<p>--London Newsroom +44 171 542 4366</p>
